{"tid":1187700,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"我個細仔真係不孝子黎","createTime":"2019-06-05T23:32:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-06T02:57:56.000Z","uid":201091,"like":67,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c7021f7b9bf37a94920e9acfbfd7d6e2a64ab6b6","tid":1187700,"uid":201091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T23:32:15.000Z","msg":"我有兩個仔<br />\n一個25歲，一個29歲<br />\n大個個到而家都未有女朋友<br />\n咁我就冇乜所謂嘅<br />\n呢d野不嬲都係講緣份<br />\n不能強求<br />\n而我個細仔呢<br />\n就有個拍咗一年施既女朋友<br />\n佢地話有買樓<br />\n問我同埋老婆借200萬<br />\n咁我初初以為佢有晒planning<br />\n答應咗佢<br />\n點知個大仔突然之間衝咗出黎<br />\n話細仔同埋女朋友加埋揾得35k個月<br />\n我打咗個突<br />\n揾得35k都想買樓<br />\n睇怕我個200萬肯定有借冇還<br />\n加上我細仔每個月俾得3k家用<br />\n遲d買咗樓後$500都唔知有冇<br />\n咁我即刻話都係考慮下先<br />\n之後我細仔不斷話[自己冇女，唔扺得我有女]<br />\n個陣時我已經知道我細仔係有異性冇人性<br />\n件事完咗後，我去咗律師樓到改遺囑<br />\n我死後，所有資產會留俾晒大仔<br />\n你一個仙都唔使旨意拿到呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不孝子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75dfc63eb14dd18682f59935ac99223576b53b99","tid":1187700,"uid":201091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T23:38:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e663981f41b3993cc1a0af0b86c89ed80c7eaf9","tid":1187700,"uid":242702,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T00:06:02.000Z","msg":"我啊哥真係好撚仆街<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1187297\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1187297</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n係呀你個細仔仲開post屌個大仔添呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c8925351566f66cd2398b50f7ec195ebcd00887","tid":1187700,"uid":201091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7e663981f41b3993cc1a0af0b86c89ed80c7eaf9","tid":1187700,"uid":242702,"l